# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:12
translate spanish brandichat11_12a15b04:

    # "I wonder if Brandi is streaming right now. I open up the Kitch website and see her stream on the front page."
    "Me pregunto si Brandi estará retransmitiendo ahora mismo. Abro la página web de Kitch y veo su retransmisión en la página principal."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:16
translate spanish brandichat11_10721f64:

    # "She's already in the middle of a conversation when I load up the stream."
    "Ya está en medio de una conversación cuando cargo la retransmisión."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:17
translate spanish brandichat11_b8ff41b7:

    # fd "No guys, we went on a for real date! Just me and him."
    fd "No, chicos, ¡hemos tenido una cita de verdad! Solo él y yo."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:18
translate spanish brandichat11_1d135968:

    # fd "Sorry I didn't bring you all along with us on this one, but I wanted some alone time, you know?"
    fd "Siento no haberos llevado a todos con nosotros esta vez, pero quería un rato a solas, ¿sabéis?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:19
translate spanish brandichat11_fb8907cd:

    # fd "I can't just stream every second of my day, as much as I'm sure you want to see that."
    fd "No puedo retransmitir cada segundo de mi día, por mucho que esté segura de que queréis verlo."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:22
translate spanish brandichat11_707868bc:

    # fd "But we went to the park and had a nice walk. We talked about a lot of things."
    fd "Pero fuimos al parque y dimos un agradable paseo. Hablamos de muchas cosas."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:23
translate spanish brandichat11_7e5ded88:

    # fd "I really like him, guys."
    fd "Me gusta mucho, chicos."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:24
translate spanish brandichat11_49344d1c:

    # fd "Like, I think this is going to get serious."
    fd "Creo que esto va a ir en serio."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:25
translate spanish brandichat11_67c29154:

    # fd "I didn't think I'd meet anybody that would make me want to get serious, but I'm thinking about him all the time."
    fd "No pensaba que conocería a nadie que me hiciera querer algo serio, pero no dejo de pensar en él."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:26
translate spanish brandichat11_0d0165ad:

    # fd "I think I might be falling for him."
    fd "Creo que me estoy enamorando de él."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:29
translate spanish brandichat11_40d00103:

    # fd "Anyways. Dinner's done, stream's over. I should start getting ready for bed."
    fd "En fin. Ya he cenado, se acabó la retransmisión. Debería empezar a prepararme para irme a la cama."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:30
translate spanish brandichat11_4ab06329:

    # fd "No, [pcname] isn't here tonight, but damn I kind of wish he was, if you know what I mean?"
    fd "No, [pcname] no está aquí esta noche, pero joder, me gustaría que estuviera, ¿sabéis a qué me refiero?"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:31
translate spanish brandichat11_c9c25f00:

    # fd "Sigh. Maybe soon."
    fd "Suspiro. Quizás pronto."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:32
translate spanish brandichat11_817d358f:

    # fd "Okay guys, thanks for watching! Catch me again next time!"
    fd "¡Vale, chicos, gracias por vernos! ¡Nos vemos la próxima vez!"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:34
translate spanish brandichat11_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/brandichat 11_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/brandichat 11_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:35
translate spanish brandichat11_b92cdc62:

    # fd "Be sure to subscribe and smash that bell icon so you'll be notified every time I go online!"
    fd "¡Aseguraos de suscribiros y darle al icono de la campana para que os avisen cada vez que me conecte!"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:37
translate spanish brandichat11_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/brandi_goodnight1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/brandi_goodnight1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:38
translate spanish brandichat11_8ef86a70:

    # fd "Good night!"
    fd "¡Buenas noches!"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:42
translate spanish brandichat11_31d20b9f:

    # "With that, she closes the stream."
    "Con eso, cierra la retransmisión."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandichat11.rpy:43
translate spanish brandichat11_c9acb08a:

    # "It seems I made quite an impression on her."
    "Parece que le he causado bastante impresión."

